Start activities with explicit intents:
- Here we will learn how to add visual controls within the content layout file to
  show a graphic and a couple of text views.
- And will show you how to navigate from the main activity to this new activity named "About".
----------------
- To navigate from one activity to another within a single app, following code is used:
Intent intent = new Intent(this, AboutActivity.class);
startActivity(intent);
----------------
- getSupportActionBar().setDisplayHomeAsUpEnabled(true);
  - This line display back button in the About activity page for older version of android.
----------------
